{"tid":319489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國國台辦：改變台灣是中國一部分 都是徒勞","createTime":"2017-07-12T23:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T07:17:58.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b1136f6ffcc373d725cbad6ac2b9f544e69a87c","tid":319489,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T23:48:33.000Z","msg":"國台辦：改變台灣是中國一部分 都是徒勞<br />\n<br />\n2017/07/12 18:13&nbsp;3676<br />\n<br />\n中國國台辦發言人馬曉光今表示，「開羅宣言」是日本在二戰投降後，中國收復台灣、澎湖等的國際法依據，<span style=\"color: red;\">「任何企圖改變『台灣是中國一部分』地位的圖謀都是徒勞的」。</span><br />\n<br />\n中央社報導，中國國務院台灣事務辦公室今下午發出新聞稿，馬曉光回應媒體詢問台灣在預定2019年實施的高中社會科新課綱不再提「開羅宣言」，作上述表示。馬曉光稱：「世界上只有一個中國，台灣是中國不可分割的一部分，具有不容置疑的歷史事實和法理基礎，也得到國際社會普遍承認。任何企圖改變『台灣是中國一部分』地位的圖謀都是徒勞的。」<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170712/1159711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170712%2F1159711&d=tn6kEAKrQafbM6FcrJe3Se9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=74c576af\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170712/1159711</a><br />\n<br />\n誤解&quot;將台灣改變成中國一部份 都是徒勞&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd33494375308dc72b73c8fa9e3d884a7da3240","tid":319489,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T23:58:36.000Z","msg":"國台辦：改變香港是中國一部分 都是徒勞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e243900406018b359ce63276a6209ddef191ec","tid":319489,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36904eb6bffcfee1a657bd4d67b1b0232e50ebde","tid":319489,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"噉似啲香港五毛話港獨不切實際？"},{"pid":"9864d57be9b1e33e0e6ed4feb410fd1c3cf97fdc","tid":319489,"uid":50457,"lik